title: Germany Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Germany increased 17.70 percent in September of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Germany averaged 1.79 percent from 1992 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 17.70 percent in September of 2022 and a record low of -3.10 percent in October of 2009. This page provides the latest reported value for - Germany Food Inflation - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Federal Statistical Office
